SEARCH
Package entities

Class Restaurant

java.lang.Object
entities.Restaurant
public class Restaurant extends Object
Represents a Restaurant entity with various attributes. Provides methods to get and set these attributes, as well as to create a Restaurant object from a string representation. Also includes a utility method to parse a string representation of multiple Restaurant objects.
Version:
August 2024
Author:
Kfir Amoyal, Israel Ohayon, Yaniv Shatil, Noam Furman, Omri Heit, Eitan Zerbel
